6
00:01:33,225 --> 00:01:34,817
Kiss 'em good-bye for me, Maury.

7
00:01:34,894 --> 00:01:37,328
I'll miss 'em...
like hell I will.

8
00:01:37,396 --> 00:01:38,385
Dreamin' again.

9
00:01:38,464 --> 00:01:40,830
Not anymore, Lil.
I'm awake now,

10
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:44,028
