Welcome to Hotel Earle.
May I help you?

156
00:08:57,636 --> 00:08:59,069
I'm checking in.

157
00:08:59,137 --> 00:09:00,399
Barton Fink.

158
00:09:00,472 --> 00:09:03,066
All righty.

159
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:06,769
Okay...

160
00:09:06,845 --> 00:09:09,109
F-I-N-K?

161
00:09:11,817 --> 00:09:12,943
"Fink, Barton."

162
00:09:13,018 --> 00:09:14,485
That must be you, huh?

163
00:09:14,553 --> 00:09:15,611
Must be.

164
00:09:15,687 --> 00:09:20,283
Okay, then everything
seems to be in order.

165
00:09:20,359 --> 00:09:23,453
Everything seems to be in order.

166
00:09:23,528 --> 00:09:24,790
