167
00:09:26,031 --> 00:09:28,829
Are you a trans or a res?

168
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:29,992
Excuse me?

169
00:09:30,068 --> 00:09:31,626
Transient or resident?

170
00:09:31,703 --> 00:09:32,795
I...

171
00:09:32,871 --> 00:09:34,805
I... I... I don't know.

172
00:09:34,873 --> 00:09:37,068
I mean, I'll be here indefinitely.

173
00:09:37,142 --> 00:09:40,009
Res. That's 25.50 a week
payable in advance.

174
00:09:40,078 --> 00:09:41,807
Check-out time's 12:00 sharp,

175
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,780
